name: Wittin
Lore: 'Male Jawa. Leader of a large tribe of Jawas. Plotting with Jabba to take control of a neighboring tribe''s territory.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. Your Jawa Pack is not unique, is doubled, deploys free (or for 6 Force from each player) and cumulatively affects your Jawa''s forfeit. While at Audience Chamber or Jawa Camp, all your other Jawas are power +2.',
